# Tailwind And Styling

Use Tailwind utilities as the primary styling approach.

## Rules

- Prefer Tailwind utility classes in component markup for local styling.
- Reuse global tokens/variables from `app/globals.css` (`background`, `foreground`, fonts).
- Avoid one-off inline styles unless dynamic values require them.
- Keep custom CSS in `globals.css` minimal and cross-cutting (tokens, resets, shared behavior).
- Preserve reduced-motion behavior for scroll/animation effects.
- Use consistent spacing and typography scales across sections/components.

## Images

- Use `next/image` in app code for static assets in `public/`.
- Provide meaningful `alt` text for informative images.
